// ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
// Memory Atoms Showcase — Wisdom/Gotcha Atoms Batch 1 (#1-#3)
//
// Demonstrates @memory_crystal + @recall_trigger + @forget_policy composing
// with @agent_memory to create a persistent, self-managing knowledge agent.
//
// Reference: proposals/WISDOM_GOTCHA_ATOMS_BATCH1_RFC.md
// ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

composition "MemoryAtomsShowcase" {

  environment {
    skybox: "gradient"
    background_color: "#020208"
    background_gradient: ["#020208", "#0a0520"]
    ambient_light: 0.15
    shadows: true
  }

  // Subtle directional light
  object "SpaceLight" {
    type: "directional_light"
    direction: [0.2, -0.6, -0.7]
    color: "#c0c8ff"
    intensity: 0.35
  }

  // ── 1. Semantic Knowledge Agent ──────────────────────────────────────────
  // A guide NPC that accumulates and recalls knowledge from interactions.
  // The @forget_policy ensures old, unused memories are pruned with audit trail.

  object "KnowledgeGuide" {
    @agent_memory(
      max_memories: 5000,
      embedding_model: "local",
      auto_compress: true
    )
    @memory_crystal(
      capacity: "semantic",
      prune_threshold: 0.85,
      backend: "kv"
    )
    @recall_trigger(
      query: "visitor question",
      min_confidence: 0.4,
      max_results: 3,
      cooldown_ms: 2000,
      trigger_on_events: ["speech_recognized", "gesture_query"],
      write_to_state: true
    )
    @forget_policy(
      after: "30d",
      when: "accessCount < 2",
      audit: true,
      eval_interval_ms: 3600000
    )
    @llm_agent(model: "claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929")
    @spatial_awareness(range: 5.0)

    model: "avatars/knowledge_guide.glb"
    position: [0, 0, -3]

    state {
      role: "knowledge_guide",
      greeting: "I remember everything visitors teach me. Ask me anything!"
    }
  }

  // ── 2. Raw Log Recorder ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
  // An environmental sensor that stores raw event data with a sliding window.
  // Uses time-window capacity for automatic TTL-based expiry.

  object "EnvironmentLogger" {
    @agent_memory(
      max_memories: 10000,
      embedding_model: "none",
      auto_compress: false
    )
    @memory_crystal(
      capacity: "time-window",
      prune_threshold: 0.9,
      backend: "kv",
      time_window_ttl: 86400000
    )
    @forget_policy(
      after: "24h",
      when: "",
      audit: false,
      eval_interval_ms: 60000,
      dry_run: false
    )
    @sensor(type: "environment", sample_rate: 1.0)

    geometry: "sphere"
    position: [5, 2, 0]
    scale: [0.3, 0.3, 0.3]
    material: { baseColor: "#00ff88", roughness: 0.3, metallic: 0.2 }
    emissive: "#00ff88"
    emissiveIntensity: 0.5

    state {
      role: "environment_logger",
      recording: true
    }
  }

  // ── 3. Curator Agent with Dry-Run Forget ─────────────────────────────────
  // A management agent that evaluates forget policies in dry-run mode,
  // allowing human review before actual deletion.

  object "MemoryCurator" {
    @agent_memory(
      max_memories: 2000,
      embedding_model: "local",
      auto_compress: true
    )
    @memory_crystal(
      capacity: "raw",
      prune_threshold: 0.7,
      backend: "kv",
      warn_unpaired: false
    )
    @recall_trigger(
      query: "audit review",
      min_confidence: 0.2,
      max_results: 10,
      cooldown_ms: 5000,
      trigger_on_events: ["curator_review_requested"]
    )
    @forget_policy(
      after: "7d",
      when: "accessCount < 1",
      audit: true,
      eval_interval_ms: 300000,
      dry_run: true,
      max_deletes_per_cycle: 50
    )
    @hitl(approval_required: true)

    model: "avatars/curator_bot.glb"
    position: [-3, 0, -2]

    state {
      role: "memory_curator",
      mode: "review",
      pending_deletions: 0
    }
  }

  // ── 4. Unpaired Crystal (Gotcha Demo) ────────────────────────────────────
  // Intentionally declares @memory_crystal WITHOUT @forget_policy to
  // demonstrate the compiler warning: "Memory may grow unbounded."

  object "UnpairedDemo" {
    @agent_memory(max_memories: 500)
    @memory_crystal(
      capacity: "raw",
      prune_threshold: 0.95,
      backend: "kv",
      warn_unpaired: true
    )

    geometry: "box"
    position: [3, 1, -4]
    scale: [0.5, 0.5, 0.5]
    material: { baseColor: "#ff4444", roughness: 0.4, metallic: 0.15 }
    emissive: "#ff4444"
    emissiveIntensity: 0.35

    state {
      note: "This object will emit a crystal_threshold_warn on attach"
    }
  }

  post_processing {
    bloom: { intensity: 0.7, threshold: 0.3, radius: 0.5 }
    tone_mapping: "aces"
  }
}
